<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="figure-v">figure <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'fɪɡə(r)/    美 /'fɪɡjər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>是重要部分；是...的部分</strong></h4>
<p>to be an important part of sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My feeling about the matter didn't seem to figure at all.
我对此事的感受似乎一点也不重要。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My wishes didn't figure among his considerations.
我的愿望不在他的考虑之中。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>认为；估计</strong></h4>
<p>to think or guess sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Figure the consequences to your life if you lose the job.
想象一下，如果你失去工作会对你的生活有什么影响吧。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>From the way he behaved, I <strong>figured</strong> (<strong>that</strong>) he was drunk.
从他的举止来看，我认为他喝醉了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3ame">3.<strong>(AmE) 计算：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'm just figuring my expenses.
我在计算我的开销。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="figure-out">figure out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>弄清楚；弄明白；计算出：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>College is when we should focus on a specific major, but high school is when we have to figure it out.
在大学时我们需要专注于某一专业，而在中学时我们需要找出这一专业。</p><footer>2015 湖南</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I couldn't figure out what I had done to annoy my boss.
我不明白自己做了什么让老板生气。</p><footer>北师大⑦ – 20</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Have you figured out how much the trip will cost?
旅行要花多少费用你算出来没有？</p><footer>2012福建</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The present situation is very complex, so I think it will take me some time to figure <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ its reality.  （2008 湖北改）<br />
B.   </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. out  </p></div>